Text: In other news, Director Wesley A. Brown sold 3,320 shares of the company's stock in a transaction dated Friday, June 21st. The shares were sold at an average price of $137.35, for a total transaction of $456,002.00. Following the transaction, the director now owns 90,931 shares in the company, valued at $12,489,372.85.
